Urue-Offong/Oruko dị na ndịda-ọwụwa anyanwụ nke Naijiria ma bụrụ mpaghara ọchịchị ime obodo nke Akwa Ibom steeti e kere na Septemba 1991

Urue-Offong/Oruko bụ otu n'ime ọchịchị obodo ise na-asụ Ọro nke dị na North West site na Okobo, Akwa Ibom, Oron, Akwa Ibom na North East, nke Udung Uko gbara n'Ebe Ọwụwa Anyanwụ, na na South East site na ya
Mbo, Akwa Ibom nakwa Esit Eket na South West nwere oke ya.
